Package dalserver.scs

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ScsMessier
    ScsMessier implements the essential functionality needed to do a simple cone search (SCS) query on the Messier catalog, which is built directly into the DALServer SCS implementation in order to provide a simple demonstration SCS service.
    ScsMessier.MessierObj
    A single object within the Messier catalog.
    ScsMessierData
    Raw data for Messier catalog (this class is autogenerated).
    ScsMySql
    ScsMySql provides a simple cone search (SCS) capability for any catalog which can be accessed via JDBC to a MySQL database.
    ScsOracle
    ScsOracle provides a simple cone search (SCS) capability for any catalog which can be accessed via JDBC to a MySQL database.
    ScsParamSet
    Construct an initial default parameter set containing the parameters for Simple Cone Search (SCS) service.
    ScsQuery
    ScsQuery provides a simple cone search (SCS) capability for any catalog which can be accessed via a JDBC database connection to a supported DBMS.
    ScsService
    A generic class which implements the operations for a DALServer SCS service.
    ScsServlet
    Generic HTTP Servlet for the Simple Cone Search (SCS) protocol.
